             was indicted for <rs id="t17960622-43-off239" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17960622-43-off239" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17960622-43-off239" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17960622-43-cd240" type="crimeDate">11th of June</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17960622-43-off239 t17960622-43-cd240"></join>, four pounds weight of sugar, value 2s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17960622-43-victim491" type="victimName">
                     William 
                     Pyecroft
                  <interp inst="t17960622-43-victim491" type="surname" value="Pyecroft"></interp>
